	<td class="bodycopy">
		<!--BODYCOPY BEGINS HERE-->
<p>
Whereas Modern-Up was a collaboration between Mario Huys and Vincent Mous (creator of the Modern variant), Slovenia is what Vincent calls <i>"a different variant"</i>. The addition of Slovenia was first proposed by Chris Fridrich and put in its definite form by Mario, who describes this in the <a href=<POUCH>>Diplomatic Pouch</A> Zine article <a href=<POUCH>/Zine/S2015R/Huys/slovenia.htm>The Modern Art of Love</a>, with a <a href=<POUCH>/Zine/F2015M/Mous/war.htm>riposte</a> by Vincent in the next Zine.

